About this item

Smart summary

Generated by AI

The Beechmore Books journal features  160 lined pages ,  8.5 x 11.5 inches  in size, with 120 GSM thick paper. It has a  hardcover leather binding ,  elastic closure , and a ribbon bookmark. The journal is designed for writing, note-taking, and creative projects, with  acid-free and bleed-resistant pages . It includes a deep back pocket for storage and comes in a gift box. The journal's college-ruled format and thick paper provide a smooth writing experience, making it suitable for various uses, including work, journaling, and creative pursuits.

About this item

Product details

Struggling to fit all your thoughts, notes, or sketches on cramped, small journal pages? Journaling is a deeply personal and creative process, and sometimes, bigger pages are essential to fully capture your thoughts and ideas. Whether you’re mapping out detailed plans, brainstorming creative projects, or drafting long-form writing, larger pages provide the space needed to think expansively without feeling restricted. Bigger pages also allow for better clarity, as you can spread out your content and review it all at a glance. With our A4 lined business office notebook, you’ll have the perfect canvas to organize your thoughts and unleash your creativity. Elevate your writing experience with the Beechmore Books A4 Leather Journal. With its luxurious 8.5x11" pages, this professional notebook offers a premium experience for those who demand both style and function. Whether you use it for work, journaling, or creative pursuits, this A4-sized planner helps you unleash your full potential. Crafted with 160 pages (80 sheets) of uniquely thicker 120gsm ivory cream paper, this executive journal provides a smooth writing surface that resists ink bleed, ghosting, and shading. No matter if you prefer fountain pens or pencils, this notepad for ideas can handle it all without compromising the integrity of your writing. The elegant hardcover is bound in vegan leather, adding style while ensuring durability. The elastic closure keeps your notes secure, and the built-in ribbon bookmark helps you easily pick up where you left off. Plus, the deep back pocket provides extra space to store receipts, notes, or business cards, making it ideal for on-the-go professionals. Here are more reasons to love our A4 lined daily planner: - Comes in a beautiful gift box - Designed in the UK - Offered in a variety of colors Go for a notebook that has the space and quality to match your creativity. Add the Beechmore Books A4 Leather Journal to your cart NOW! Each journal boasts 160 lined pages, providing ample space for your writing endeavors. The college-ruled format ensures neat and organized writing, while the thick, high-quality paper offers a smooth writing experience. Encased in a durable hardcover and bound in luxurious leather, our journals exude sophistication and durability. Perfect for travelers, professionals, students, and anyone in between, our journals are designed to accompany you on all of life's adventures. Capture your thoughts, ideas, and memories in style with Beechmore Books' A4 Leather Journals. Whether you're exploring new places or simply seeking inspiration, our journals are your reliable companions. Elevate your writing experience and make every moment count with Beechmore Books. Order now and embark on a journey of creativity, organization, and self-expression.
